These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: almond-milk, soy-milk, iced-tea, coffee
Sport: rowing, biathlon, cricket, skiing
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the right of Sport:cricket##1
2. Sport:skiing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:cricket is between Sport:biathlon and Beverage:soy-milk##2
4. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:iced-tea is between Beverage:soy-milk and Beverage:almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee         | soy-milk   | iced-tea | almond-milk       |
| Sport      | skiing | rowing | cricket   | biathlon |

