.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: filmmaking, dancing, hiking, fishing
Nationality: argentine, american, pakistani, australian
1. Nationality:australian is between Hobby:hiking and Nationality:american##2
2. Hobby:fishing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:pakistani is on the right of Nationality:argentine##1
4. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | dancing | filmmaking | hiking | fishing |
| Nationality   | american    | australian   | argentine | pakistani       |

