2. Nationality:argentine is between Nationality:dutch and Food:pomegranate##2
3. Nationality:dutch is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:russian is on the left of Food:asparagus##1
5. Food:pomegranate == Nationality:russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | tomato    | garlic | pomegranate   | asparagus  |
| Nationality   | dutch | argentine   | russian | malaysian |

